Class ElementPropertyPane

java.lang.Object

                          +--com.esri.mo2.ui.lyt.ElementPropertyPane
All Implemented Interfaces:
Accessible, ImageObserver, MenuContainer, Serializable, SwingConstants
public abstract class ElementPropertyPane
extends JTabbedPane

A base class to show an element's properties. It defines two default property panes, Frame Pane and Postion & Size Pane. It must be sub-classed even if you don't want the two default property panes. Notes: you normally need to call setPreferredSize() to set up a right size for the particular property pane.
